       The first line of output gives the easting (E) and northing (N) coordi-
       nates of the geographic location at which the user clicked  the  mouse.
       The  subsequent  two  lines  give the map name and mapset, map category
       value (within parentheses), and map  category  label  corresponding  to
       this  user-selected  map  location, for each of the maps queried by the
       user.


