       _d_._w_h_a_t_._r_a_s_t output can be redirected into a file; however,  if  it  is,
       the  output  will  go both to the screen and to the file.  For example:
       dd..wwhhaatt..rraasstt mmaapp==_s_o_i_l_s_,_a_s_p_e_c_t >> wwhhaatt..oouutt

       will both send _d_._w_h_a_t_._r_a_s_t output to the screen and capture its  output
       in the file named _w_h_a_t_._o_u_t.


       The maximum number of raster map layers that can be queried at one time
       is 15.


